 Team Bike Server

- Local server and MacApp that allows the user to poll from the NXT sensors. This is exported as a JSON and is accessible at localhost/TeamBikeServer.

Setup:

- Install XAMPP

- Copy the folder "TeamBikeServer" to "/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/"

- Launch XAMPP and start Apache web server

- Launch LegoNXTRemote application

- Select connect button on LegoNXTRemote app

- Select NXT1

Server Output

- The output from the server can be viewed at localhost/TeamBikeServer


